Richard Travis (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Travis_(actor) 0 Not to be confused with the actor Richard Travis (born 1955), whose film credits since the 1980s have been mistakenly merged with those of this actor.
Richard Travis (born William Benton Justice, April 17, 1913 – July 11, 1989) was an American actor in films and television. Not to_be_confused with the_actor_Richard_Travis ( born 1955 ) , whose_film_credits since the_1980s have_been_mistakenly_merged with those of this_actor .
